        "title": "feat(claworks): white-label stage A and runtime/evolution product layer",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nClaWorks product layer on top of OpenClaw upstream — **185 commits** on `local/claworks-product`.\n\n### White-label (Stage A)\n- Studio shell refresh (`studio/index.html`, README) and product-aware doctor hints\n- Wizard/setup product copy, i18n, and security-note alignment\n- CLI productization across doctor, plugins, gateway, configure, and onboarding flows\n- Product copy audit script and docs alignment (`docs/claworks/install.md`, release/signoff checklists)\n\n### Runtime & evolution\n- `packages/claworks-runtime`: EventKernel, PlaybookMatcher, evolve-engine, sandbox playbook runner\n- Evolution pipeline: draft promote gate (requires `simulation.passed`), weak-model regression suite, export/import REST\n- Smoke/audit scripts: evolution chain, gateway e2e, KB ingest/import, OT connectivity\n- Integration hub, ontology bootstrap, autonomy engine, CBR, and REST endpoints (`/v1/doctor`, `/v1/events/stream`, etc.)\n\n### Docs & CI\n- ClaWorks operator runbooks (Feishu live e2e, OT live, branch protection, npm publish)\n- CI gates for Feishu live e2e and weak-model regression\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] `pnpm test packages/claworks-runtime/src/kernel/evolve-engine.test.ts`\n- [ ] `pnpm test packages/claworks-runtime/src/claworks/product-config-repair.test.ts`\n- [ ] `node scripts/claworks-evolution-chain-smoke.mjs` (sandbox)\n- [ ] `pnpm test test/scripts/claworks-weak-model-regression-gate.test.ts`\n- [ ] `pnpm test src/wizard/product-copy.test.ts`\n- [ ] `openclaw doctor` on a ClaWorks-branded config — verify product hints and studio doctor status\n- [ ] Manual Studio load (`studio/index.html`) — branding and doctor panel render\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: ClaWorks KB audit script, evolve draft REST gateway e2e coverage, CLI product copy (batch 7), install/doctor docs.\n\nReal environment tested: macOS 15 dev checkout (`/Users/power/Projects/claworks`), Node 24, `CLAWORKS_PRODUCT=1`.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch:\n```\nCLAWORKS_PRODUCT=1 node claworks.mjs --version\nnode scripts/claworks-kb-audit-openclaw.mjs --kb-root <temp-kb-tree>\npnpm claworks:runtime:test\n```\n\nEvidence after fix:\n```\n$ CLAWORKS_PRODUCT=1 node claworks.mjs --version\nClaWorks 0.0.0 (3420f17)\n\n$ node scripts/claworks-kb-audit-openclaw.mjs --kb-root /tmp/kb-audit-sample\n[kb-audit] kb_root=/tmp/kb-audit-sample\n=== KB Audit Summary ===\nMD files: 1\n  product_manual → products: 1 md, source=1, ocr=0, truncated=1\nScores: linkage=100% index_align=100% ocr_placeholder=0%\nfile_index: 1 entries, missing_from_index=0, orphan=0\n```\n\nObserved result after fix: ClaWorks CLI reports product branding; KB audit script scans a real filesystem tree and prints category stats, index alignment, and ontology gap recommendations without modifying content.\n\nWhat was not tested: Full `pnpm claworks:gateway:e2e` (~90s) and OT live hardware on this push; evolution chain smoke not re-run locally for this batch.\n\n## Notes\n\n- Base: `main` (upstream OpenClaw).\n\nMade with [Cursor](https://cursor.com)",
